metadata.name: Incanto 1
metadata.description:
Incanto 1  
    
None like silk as though pillars and are  
Patterned servants of fateâ€™s stone;  
The western canopy and baptistry  
Down, without tend.  
                            
The identity appears, distorted at first  
Who by firelit mask gazed on a  
Necklaced and prodigal Odysseus;  
Here on woven earth.

And yet, since birth the marble dark itself  
Underground and without mortal belief  
Lying still, observes the named hour.

Created: 2/2/2022  
Author: Oxen
